text: I think I have solved the QUANTUM problem, and the link to SPECTRE.  It's SMERSH.  SMERSH was the original soviet organization behind everything in majority of Fleming's novels, long before SPECTRE (which didn't come into play until the novel Thunderball).  In the bond movies, they replaced SMERSH with SPECTRE.  SMERSH is only mentioned twice, and both times it is a ruse.  I am thinking that QUANTUM has taken SMERSH's place.  However, due to the events of Casino Royale, QOS, and Skyfall, QUANTUM has fallen or has weakened.  But as we can see that when you just remove one evil, another emerges (like in the Middle-East).  SPECTRE is that new evil.  It is stronger than QUANTUM, deeper rooted, and has no allegiances to no one.  But then there's one more thing, the leader . . . Bond's adopted brother . . . BLOFELD!!!  Yes, I am calling it.  Just like 006 and 007 in Goldeneye, they grew up together.  However, something happened (murder? jail? insane asylum?), and Bond's brother became but a fleeting memory . . . or so he thought . . .

text: If I go to see this film only to find out that the writers kept the lame plot that was leaked for this film during the Sony breach, where "Oberhauser" is revealed to be Blofeld, and then Blofeld tells Bond that he is his brother or half-brother, I may very contemplate walking out after that. NONE of that foolishness is true to the Bond series, and quite frankly, seems to be more of an insult to the series' past than an honor or tribute. The Blofeld of yesteryear would never say something like that. Whoever even thought that such a script would've been a good idea for the Bond series needs to either re-watch all of the films (no matter how bad or good) or be shown the door. Lame scripts like this only further tarnish what is an overall great series. Oh and although Skyfall was a very nice improvement over Quantum of Solace, it was nowhere near as great as Casino Royale.

text: Ian Flemming, whom wrote the James Bond books, was a known satanist.. in fact, his best friend in the world was pedophile and founder of modern satanism "Aleister Crowley" ... He actually wrote the character "Le Cheafe" (the villain in Casino Royale) to be Crowley... as a way to pay homage to the pedophile satanist. Ian Flemming also supported Hitler's nazism, even though he was in the British Intelligence... and the name "007" comes from occultism, as it was Dr. John Dee whom worked for Queen Elizabeth in the 1500's (he was into witchcraft, occultism), and he signed his name "007" as a double agent for multiple nations, as their "occultist" whom mapped out their futures by star gazing. A practice condemned by God of the Bible.

text: 'Oberhauser taught climbing and skiing in KitzbÃ¼hel before World War II. He even taught James Bond during his youth while he was on term breaks while attending Fettes College. He formed a very strong paternal relationship with James, to such an extent that he later referred to him as his second father. After the annexation of Austria and outbreak of war with Great Britain he was drafted into the Gestapo, probably due to his ability to speak English.  One day, in the closing weeks of the war, a British officer arrived by jeep at Oberhauser's chalet and arrested him. He had told his weeping, protesting family that he was being taken to an interrogation camp in Munich. If the Oberhauser's record was clean he would be released within a week. If his family caused a drama it would just make things worse for Oberhauser.  The officer and Oberhauser drove off and Oberhauser was told that in exchange for assisting him climbing the Kaiser range, he would report to his commanding officer that he had been cleared at Munich. He guided the Englishman up the mountain to a hut where he was shot point blank in the back of the skull by the officer's Webley & Scott .45 pistol. His body was then pushed off the mountain onto a glacier below.  Twenty years later, Oberhauser's corpse was discovered by mountaineers and the case for his murder was re-opened. As serendipity had it, the case was noticed by James Bond, who set out to discover the one responsible for his friend's death". (An extract from Octopussy novel of Ian fleming)

With Christoph Waltzâ€™s alluring, soothing but at the same time sinister voice just adds to the mystery and anticipation surrounding his character and the role that he is to play. For is he the head of Spectre or merely a supporting General???  One thingÂ for certain is that Spectre will surpass Skyfall as the most successful film in the Bond franchise.  Roll on November 2015

text: I've always wondered why the scrips for James Bond are so awful. "Skyfall" for example was so incoherent and out of reality that we could easily deduce that it was more suited to 13-year olds than a 25-55 year old crowd.  The only bond movie I can recall, with an acceptable script, was "Casino Royale". There is so much potential here for having a great, realistic series. For an action scene to be great, one doesn't have to explode a planet and survive out of a ridiculous situation (remember bond jumping on a cliff in order to reach a plain which was heading downwards... First scene in Goldeneye IIRC. You don't have to be a physicist to understand that it's unnatural to reach that plain which is heading with a fully working engine downwards). I don't know, it ruins the movie for me.  What do you think about it?

text: A short time ago, I've sent an email to Bob Iger about Walt Disney Pictures to buy James Bond following the news of Sony Pictures to retire distribution rights to 007:   Dear Robert A. Iger,  My name is Callum Precious and I'm come from the UK but I just heard the news that Sony to retire distribution rights to the Bond films after the release of Spectre this November. I only understand that The Walt Disney Company will buy James Bond, a spy movie franchise that spanned for over 50 years. To myself that Warner Bros' distribution rights to 007 is very unlikely but it is likely that 007 franchise will go into Walt Disney Pictures; much like Marvel and Lucasfilm. The ideal of Disney's acquisition of the franchise goes into my head since 2013, and to make sure that Disney to be a #1 bidder to buy the world's most successful franchise from Sony. Meaning that Disney will reunite with MGM since 1985 because they entered a licencing contract to form a Disney World called 'Disney-MGM Studios' (now Disney's Hollywood Studios) and was officially opened on May 1st 1989. Thank you and i wilko hope that is going to happen this Christmas :-)  Your Sincerely  Callum Precious

text: These films have always fascinated me for one reason: the idea of there being secret organizations that not even the CIA or MI-6 know about. As an aspiring Nietzsche scholar, I have always asked myself 'where have the strong gone? where does power truly reside?' Now this may seem like an overly normative, fanboy theory, but I like to think that the strong have become so impossibly powerful that they're unrecognizable even to the most perceptive individuals. In our times, it is not the physically superior and apparently threatening that are best able to bend people to their will, but rather, the deceitful. In Plato's dialogue 'Gorgias', Socrates confronts the craft of oratory (manipulation through persuasion) and is told by its master Calicles that it is the art of getting people to do whatever you want. But what's interesting about the dialogue is that Calicles does not confront Socrates until his two students Gogias and Polous (his henchmen) have been dispensed with, instead, he waits in relative silence while assessing Socrates. As i understand it, SPECTER is responsible for training many of Bonds adversaries in Counter-intelligence, terrorism, extortion and so on. In the context of the Bond trilogy, perhaps SPECTER is our Calicles, while Quantum and Skyfall, despite there brilliance, are mere henchmen; subsidiary players. I do not doubt the plausibility of there being secret players such as these in the real world, people with anti-ethical and impersonal motives who conduct themselves ubiquitously and are the closest thing to power personified. But what's important to keep in mind though is that when power is so condensed, so concentrated, it begins to lose any and all identity...something external to all men, where even characters such as the one portrayed by Christopher Waltz, are merely its puppets.

text: ciao chiarisco l'ideea con la monomania ..in tanti modi io posso voler bene o amare persone..nessuno ed obligato ad amarmi oppure sposarmi(non ho fretta su questo capitolo..bisogna conoscere alquni tipi..etc)la fretta e capire dove sono gli soldini perche sono necesari..ad exempio devo cercare un avocato per vedere se la polizia di questa cita si occupa del indagine perche a me non dicono niente e mi servono soldi anche per questo..scarpe non ho..etc...e oddioso chiedere aiuto anche esterno(cioe a te..per fare domande a bucarest e tutto ..chi sa cosa decidono li..visto che gli fa impazzire avere supervisori anche su questioni musica..e non solo)..in un certo modo ed al di la di ogni cosa deve sapere di me anche altra autorita oppure citadino europeo..nessuno puo negarmi questo dirritto a me oppure a te o ad altri raggazzi(the image dragons) di parlare le verita ...malgrado le antipatie e problemi  io ho scelto di scriverti non per ipocrisia que
author: cosmina hornoiu

text: quella la uso in altri casi..ma perche ti considero amico ed e giusto per me chiedere un parere piu sano.a te..etc..adesso  devi capire che mi devono soldi sai come e canti gli miei pezzi(sia)ma non mi mandi soldi per me,personalmente..e  cretina?..non ho oblighi verso begia(ripetto finche spacco cervelli il gesto panama e sufficente all nivello debbiti esterni va be che loro sarebbero capaci di molte cose ..amazarmi gli bambini..perche ho buttato questa crochetta ..ma se il mio figlio sarebbe fatto con un inglese) c'e roba da maniconio....fai in modo di finire in fretta il processo(sai  tutti dirano che non sapevano che erano rubate ,le canzoni) a me non mi piace il litiggio se la kovesi e la corte hanno visuto cosi con parazitii con me non e cosi io voglio vedere che non mi fa torto a me ..a robbie williams etc(ti rendi conto quanta gobba hanno gli le menti malate romene)..sottolineo caro amico..voglio un po bene romania..mi voglio bene a me e vi voglio bene anche a voi..percio ti ho chiesto aiuto per non perdermi..e non perdere soldi...lo stato romeno dovrebbe avere anche lui un parere sano(tariceanu..od altri)perche anche l'ideea della crema gerovital cu mac (non so la traduzione mac uguale a cosa in italiano ma ha proprieta rilasanti)e bene fino ad oggi non ho risposta  a le mie domande...voglio vivere ..a me molte persone da queste parti non piacciono piu ...insisto con te ..e non voglio stancarti perche neanche oggi nessuno non sa..non sano cosa fare....e semplice voglio la mia parte..io ho cantato ..da me sono partite varie iniziative..sthatman jeson(il americano)non ha raggione inutile guardarmi e dirmi traditrice..alla fine erano soldi di gente di europa..non potesso sopportare una cosa cosi ..come non soporto manco oggi cio che fanno con le mie canzoni idee...etc..voglio rimanere in amicizia con te ed altri...(la scuadra kovesi -ciolos -parazitii..non la voglio ma non di oggi ..da 2015 dopo eurovisione e poi gli brutti fatti non solo verso me ma anche gli altri...loro veramente sono capaci anche oggi nascondere cose soldi(oppure se li dici di prendere..10aerei spaziali e capace di farlo.. non capisce il limite quell sacco brutto senza fondo e cervello)ma addesso basta con parrolace...ti ringrazio per la pazienza ed spero in bene..ho paura..continuero a scriverti ..finche potro se mi negano anche questo guai a loro..ciao
author: cosmina hornoiu

text: devi sapere che ho personalita segmentaria non e cancro ..in piu amo la vita..puo sembrare ridicolo cio che dico  perche non molti uomini gradiscono questo tipo di logistica..perche significa anche logica :ti faccio un ex.: sull segmento casa e brucciato il tv..sul segmento salute  o scoperto a bucarest un problemino alla tiroide..etc..il segmento amore..ho deciso di conservare l'amore per me finche trovero un tipo piacevole...capisci..amico..mi piaciono le persone con testa e gesti..a volte posso anche io fare gesti..adesso ho un tappetto di segni di domanda e curiosita per questa situazione..ed ho paura(pur essendo parenti di sangue in zona)loro non sano come si gestisce la facenda su internet oppure quanto mi deve la coca cola con lime visto che lo ho riportata in vita in romania e lo stato qualche cosa incassa..caro amico..non rinuncio...ti chiedo di non rinunciare...non voglio amarezze ne per me ..te..e gli atri
